CLINICAL TRIAL PROTOCOL
Trial ID: ONCO-KRAS-502
Title: A Phase 3 Study of Next-Generation KRAS Inhibitor in Advanced NSCLC
Inclusion Criteria:
- Histologically confirmed Stage IV NSCLC.
- Documented KRAS G12C mutation.
- Progression on or after platinum-based chemotherapy and PD-1/PD-L1 inhibitor.
- Measurable disease by RECIST 1.1.
Exclusion Criteria:
- Untreated CNS metastases.
- Active second malignancy.
Logistics Support:
This trial implements the MarkovHealth logistics engine. Patients are eligible for at-home genomic testing and mobile clinical unit visits for monthly assessments.
Contact: Dr. Alistair Vance, Lead Investigator
